Description: Easily define a Nonlinear Mixed-Effects Model,
    perform a posthoc fit for a virtual subject, and
    explore new dosing regimen in a user-defined search space.
    Finally, select the best dose and evaluate future target attainment.
    A shiny app can be created by using the `shinytdmore` package.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: assertthat, mnormt, dplyr, numDeriv, stats, RxODE (>= 0.9.0), nlmixr (>= 1.1.0-9), deSolve, ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0), magrittr,
  gridExtra, zoo, rlang, purrr, Matrix, mvnfast, data.table, optimr, optextras, tibble
